NAUSICAA_SIZEOF_TEST([UINT],[unsigned int])
@end example

@noindent
the following determines the size of the field @code{l_start} in the
structure @code{struct flock} (defined in @file{fcntl.h}) and stores it
in the output variable @code{SIZEOF_STRUCT_FLOCK_L_START}:

@example
NAUSICAA_SIZEOF_FIELD_TEST([OFFSETOF_STRUCT_FLOCK_L_START],
   [struct flock],
   [l_start])
@end example


